{"url": "https://people.com/tv/kim-zolciak-biermann-kroy-hugh-hufner-playboy-bunny-costumes/", "text": "Kim Zolciak Biermann is making Hugh Hefner proud.\n\nJust days ahead of Halloween, the Real Housewives of Atlanta star served up sassy and sexy with her husband, Kroy, who together dressed up in Playboy-themed costumes.\n\n\u201cSo fun! \ud83d\ude0d\ud83d\ude0d In honor of an icon @hughhefner my gorgeous hubby @kroybiermann is channeling you tonight \ud83d\ude4f\ud83c\udffc and Im channeling one of my fav Playmates of all time @tiffallon \ud83d\ude0d\u201d wrote Kim, who channeled Playmate Tiffany Fallon.\n\n\u201cTHANK YOU @vintageinspiredbyjackie for making this perfect \u201cPlayboy Bunny\u201d costume It\u2019s a Dream! First time Kroy and I have EVER dressed up so fun #RHOAFinale #Pray4Me \ud83d\ude1d\u201d the 39-year-old wrote.\n\nIn three images shared to Instagram, the mother of six showed off her svelte figure in a black Playboy bunny costume \u2014 complete with heels, fishnets, a bowtie and ears \u2014 while standing beside Kroy, who channeled Hefner with a red robe and white sailor cap, which the late Playboy founder famously wore. (Hefner passed away in September at the age of 91.)\n\nKim Zolciak Biermann/Instagram\n\nBut Kim and Kroy aren\u2019t the only family members who have coordinated for the Oct. 31 holiday!\n\nFor Halloween 2016, the Don\u2019t Be Tardy star\u2019s 3-year-old twins \u2014 daughter, Kaia Rose, and son, Kane Ren \u2014 wore themed costumes together.\n\nThe siblings dressed up as Grease\u2018s Sandy (played by Olivia Newton-John) and Danny (played by John Travolta), complete with all-black shirts, pants and leather jackets.\n\n\u201cSandy and Danny. thx @nikitpressley for the costume idea! She picked last year and this year,\u201d Kim captioned one of many Instagram photos of her twins dressed as the musical film\u2019s characters.\n\nThe Real Housewives of Atlanta returns Nov. 5 at 8 p.m. ET on Bravo.", "images": ["https://people.com/thmb/nYmcOktpQrHyO63oU72w5TIHfas=/282x188/filters:no_upscale():max_bytes(150000):strip_icc():focal(377x120:379x122)/kim-zolciak-biermann-daughters-brielle-ariana-052223-6c2d034581df4f2db00e0417c26b6020.jpg", "https://people.com/thmb/ngM3NgbSqiY_288Cc_x_fzbMgM0=/282x188/filters:no_upscale():max_bytes(150000):strip_icc():focal(749x0:751x2)/Kim-Zolciak-game-room-031323-1-3d86c4d2e5294dbc9895ea3da035eca8.jpg", "https://people.com/thmb/lsnaiDTPKRP6eWii4qmekjU4-Ec=/282x188/filters:no_upscale():max_bytes(150000):strip_icc():focal(499x99:501x101)/breielle-ariana-biermann-110922-8ef3a1db3e4e48f287bb9f512241b1d8.jpg", "https://people.com/thmb/QAq26qYYteyrQ1cgU1Tr1c5iyGs=/282x188/filters:no_upscale():max_bytes(150000):strip_icc():focal(749x0:751x2)/Kim-Zolciak-Biermann-Is-Ready-to-Move-On-from-Ex-Kroy-0517123-d71e3d9dce974f82b5ce9267d270cda0.jpg", "https://people.com/thmb/aoI4ustjb3cSJcXTBjKudyezwh4=/282x188/filters:no_upscale():max_bytes(150000):strip_icc():focal(749x0:751x2)/kim-kardashian-met-gala-tout-0405-396572c16cbc458c91918118b6e77f33.jpg", "https://people.com/thmb/soFyxK-8zoCoQhiH6W0gFojczWI=/282x188/filters:no_upscale():max_bytes(150000):strip_icc():focal(528x301:530x303)/dont-be-c971ad96485f4d93934f43d95915cee5.jpg", "https://people.com/thmb/otBwsdLZeE8XXJphL8YaqnzFXKY=/1500x0/filters:no_upscale():max_bytes(150000):strip_icc():focal(801x0:803x2)/kim-zolciak-biermann-2-1-2000-0275899a7d434a038e9b12c1315e7a6c.jpg", "https://people.com/thmb/7lv-kZj0XUALqI9LDYSoVD-5XcY=/282x188/filters:no_upscale():max_bytes(150000):strip_icc():focal(719x559:721x561)/Kim-Zolciak-Biermann-mansion-03-021723-6eb4c5567d974006807ebc2c29b2f2b3.jpg", "https://people.com/thmb/5iUXbT-msg2z9rLIA4fDVjfWqAA=/282x188/filters:no_upscale():max_bytes(150000):strip_icc():focal(539x0:541x2)/kim-zociak-seemingly-back-to-filming-062323-47e9520e0e5b4486af7ec4c3ce20d46f.jpg", "https://people.com/thmb/5vB3uIj-sOPrVTRAnSK2LfWfcvY=/282x188/filters:no_upscale():max_bytes(150000):strip_icc():focal(734x9:73